    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get ready to roll your way into fun and challenging levels in Marble Quest, where precision, speed, and strategy are your keys to victory!<br> <br>Control your marble as it races through vibrant, ever-changing environments, dodging obstacles, finding shortcuts, and collecting gems and mastery gems along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Master the movement, and engage in thrilling races to the finish line! </i><br><i>Each level is a unique challenge, with twists and turns that will keep you on the edge of your seat.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll through a variety of creative and dynamic levels, each with its own set of challenges.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against times on the global leaderboards, and engage in exciting levels, to see who reaches the finish first!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master speed boosts and tricky terrain to gain the upper hand.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather gems to add more marbles to your collection, and uncover a new favorite as you go~</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The race to the finish starts now in Marble Quest!</p></li></ul>",
